{
  "text": "To evaluate the proposed Recall Loss (Eq. 20) derived from RaMBO we run experiments for image retrieval on the CUB-200-2011 [CITATION_1] , Stanford Online Products [CITATION_2] , and In-shop Clothes [CITATION_3] benchmarks. We compare against a variety of methods from recent years, multiple of which achieve state-of-the-art performance. The best-performing methods are ABE-8 [CITATION_4] , FastAP [CITATION_5] , and Proxy NCA [CITATION_6] .",
  "correct_citation": {
